{"ts":"2026-06-27T01:00:24.384Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Assessing the Aesthetic**\n\nI'm now diving deep into the preflight audit, focusing on aesthetic and narrative alignment. The design feels undeniably premium and custom, moving far beyond generic AI/SaaS templates. It sports a dark, glassmorphic palette with brand-specific glow accents, bespoke SVGs, and a unique authentication process. The overall narrative is also clear. I'm excited by this.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T01:00:26.170Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Evaluating Visual Harmony**\n\nI'm checking that the Control Center maintains visual thinking. The SVG lattice topology is fully accessible and interactive, highlighting nodes and updating telemetry dynamically. The theme is inherited, but tailored, using InnerPageShell and layout principles to deliver a distinct dashboard experience and high-security platform feel. I'm also finding that box-inside-box layouts are avoided.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T01:00:27.708Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Confirming Authentic Data**\n\nI'm verifying the authenticity of data and avoiding common design pitfalls. I'm pleased to report that the project uses badges sparingly and contextually, favoring plain, monospaced fonts for plan types and node statuses. Furthermore, the dashboard avoids fake elements, using abstract system telemetry and real-time logs instead of mock data or client logos. Interactions are useful and numerous, including an interactive authentication scan, twelve tabs in the client workspace, and a dynamic SVG Lattice Topology node selector.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T01:00:29.448Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Validating Mobile Experience**\n\nI'm now extremely confident about the mobile experience. Tailwind grids ensure responsive layouts, with panels wrapping elegantly on smaller screens. Spacing, typography, and visual hierarchy are all polished, and line heights are impeccable. Navigability and keyboard support are also robust. Finally, I confirmed that I have inspected all relevant files within `app/portal` and `app/client`.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
